title: Worst Date Wednesday: If You Give a Moose a Muffin
description: Bethany tells us about the guy she met at a block party that picked her up with a car that had the passenger side window missing, claimed he wasn't hungry but then ate her food, and proceeded to invited himself in for 3 HOURS when he dropped her off.
